{"tid":2254134,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾沛枝感激國泰「豐富了人生」 盤點15個藝人曾任空中服務員","createTime":"2020-10-22T15:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T12:18:34.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"831bf41220162095ea6382d66a47444541df3012","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:08:05.000Z","msg":"肺炎疫情影響下，國泰公布集團全球削減8500個職位，而旗下擁有35年歷史的港龍更即時結業。國泰稱將裁減約5300名以港為基地員工，同時將尋求由國泰本部以及旗下廉航分支快運（HK Express）接手港龍航線，港龍航空正式「走進歷史」。"},{"pid":"762414cd7a77c76caae00fd9ddf389ca0236ab20","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wk57418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwk57418.jpg&h=b0876930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港龍航空於1985年創立。"},{"pid":"6b9f09a087374b734cb49b780bdf00e707ce9965","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":10,"dislike":30,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:08:28.000Z","msg":"由於事出突然，唔少員工都表示難以接受，「一覺瞓醒成間公司消失」，心情非常沉重。曾經任職國泰航空地勤兼形象大使嘅前港姐鍾沛枝，噚日亦有出Post「悼念」舊東家：「不經不覺已離開國泰航空接近10年了，感謝您CX, 豐富了我的人生🦋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/phpuFriuQ_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2FphpuFriuQ_600.jpg&h=9250b11c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/122146999_655608001810987_3370102178233869711_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2F122146999_655608001810987_3370102178233869711_n_600.jpg&h=f56cde03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n空姐一直係唔少人趨之若騖嘅職業，仲有一個「都市傳說」指擔任該職位的其中一個條件就係外貌要娟好，而香港更有唔少藝人喺加入娛樂圈前，都曾經任職空中服務員！"},{"pid":"717db275875e5ae7b3dce916a865f1146a536457","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:08:41.000Z","msg":"1.趙雅芝<br />\n<br />\n1973年，中五畢業幾年的趙雅芝，參選TVB首屆舉辦的《香港小姐競選》並獲得第四名，之後為入行辭去日本航空公司空姐一職。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/nq4000676nq1r0328qq_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2Fnq4000676nq1r0328qq_600.jpg&h=4f40fe25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19901bfe3d4c3f490856d7928f58cb1ba12b9657","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":14,"dislike":6,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"2.譚小環<br />\n<br />\n譚小環曾在國泰航空擔任空姐。後來1994年參選港姐並奪得冠軍，之後加入無綫開展演藝生涯。"},{"pid":"60db8519d502bee71ee1c99503b38b68f59da41d","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":113,"dislike":3,"score":110,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:09:06.000Z","msg":"3.吳海昕<br />\n<br />\n吳海昕畢業後曾經任職國泰航空空姐，之後參選2014年港姐，在比賽期間一直被視為冠軍大熱，可惜最後三甲不入。今年因為於ViuTV劇集《二月廿九》，演出Yeesa一角而備受關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/003205bo5ks1bsposujkj7_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2F003205bo5ks1bsposujkj7_600.jpeg&h=fe24840f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f904caf3f110ff945f412aff5da30de5975d9c87","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:09:18.000Z","msg":"4.陸詩韻<br />\n<br />\n2005年港姐亞軍陸詩韻，加入娛樂圈前做過四年空姐，分別服務過三年韓國航空公司及一年英國航空公司。"},{"pid":"6546449ea62b756dec0b084fe84672b5a610265e","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":7,"dislike":13,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:09:29.000Z","msg":"5.陳倩揚<br />\n<br />\n2008年香港小姐亞軍陳倩揚，精通日語，入行前曾任職國泰航空空姐。"},{"pid":"6f1667031a54a52f73bbdcec17a90c0ada0ca6db","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":112,"score":-109,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:09:41.000Z","msg":"6.劉佩玥<br />\n<br />\n2013年港姐季軍劉佩玥，自言做空姐令佢增廣見聞，一定程度成為佢日後參選港姐嘅動力。"},{"pid":"2f8357341d5117d869fca45ba0cb93d0ef3a7301","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":70,"score":-66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:09:56.000Z","msg":"7.李旻芳<br />\n<br />\n「東張女神」李旻芳，參加《2012年度香港小姐競選》首輪面試前，曾是空中服務員，2013年入讀第26期無綫電視藝員訓練班。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/14702376_537680116422769_4160136602059301237_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2F14702376_537680116422769_4160136602059301237_n_600.jpg&h=1ab6ebfd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9a3e929f7feac5fbcae44098d4db14d50a5973e","tid":2254134,"uid":76078,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"60db8519d502bee71ee1c99503b38b68f59da41d","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":113,"dislike":3,"score":110,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:09:06.000Z","msg":"3.吳海昕<br />\n<br />\n吳海昕畢業後曾經任職國泰航空空姐，之後參選2014年港姐，在比賽期間一直被視為冠軍大熱，可惜最後三甲不入。今年因為於ViuTV劇集《二月廿九》，演出Yeesa一角而備受關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/003205bo5ks1bsposujkj7_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2F003205bo5ks1bsposujkj7_600.jpeg&h=fe24840f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:10:08.000Z","msg":"呢個堅正"},{"pid":"dd3a78278f6907c4c3015f1c5c3c419fe3eafd92","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":46,"dislike":5,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:10:10.000Z","msg":"8.郭羨妮<br />\n<br />\n郭羨妮大學畢業，後加入國泰航空當空姐。1999年參加港姐競選，以大熱姿態獲得冠軍、「最上鏡小姐」、「國際親善小姐」和「千禧才智小姐」獎項。翌年在《國際華裔小姐競選》中，亦以大熱姿態取得冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/U5913P28T3D3676305F326DT20120704192103_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2FU5913P28T3D3676305F326DT20120704192103_600.jpeg&h=c6301c3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b10bb4dd143ad3313a0c053b9615d9b79a8dbc8b","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":112,"score":-108,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:10:21.000Z","msg":"9.朱智賢<br />\n<br />\n朱智賢曾是國泰、港龍空姐，2013年參選港姐，20強止步，入行成為無綫藝人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/20190530085806_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2F20190530085806_600.jpg&h=28452605&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a140babd390ac395fdbca77ec40189a5ec557a30","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":11,"dislike":57,"score":-46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:10:33.000Z","msg":"10.黃智雯<br />\n<br />\n黃智雯就讀香港演藝學院，取得舞蹈及戲劇系表演藝術文憑，後於國泰航空做過3年空姐，2007年參加《香港小姐競選》打入最後五強。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/369314f_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2F369314f_600.jpg&h=b0d6d0bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71b12c9cf9097fbe79ed2d69979c477ca4323635","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":40,"dislike":6,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"11.李若彤<br />\n<br />\n「最美小龍女」李若彤讀到中六之後，放棄繼續升學，1986年於國泰航空任職空中服務員，後被星探發掘拍廣告，輾轉加入娛樂圈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/12f1e4a257712da68ec98b13984a2b81saasftp20200221_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2F12f1e4a257712da68ec98b13984a2b81saasftp20200221_600.jpg&h=f676a20f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dba1beafb000391a56fbb8c3fdb170829327181","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":10,"dislike":47,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:11:01.000Z","msg":"12.林淑敏<br />\n<br />\n「大小姐」林淑敏於多倫多大學修讀電影研究，1999年畢業。之後做過電視台及製作公司的製作助理、副導演，後來又做咗7個月空組 ; 再以選港姐為跳板，加入TVB。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/cf3e2ee1287edc3a7bdffae4e3961c03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2Fcf3e2ee1287edc3a7bdffae4e3961c03_600.jpg&h=b55350f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b71cc620ff3d31d67e0047ff75aa471809b6953f","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":16,"dislike":16,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"13.蔡明思<br />\n<br />\nJessica@Super Girls（蔡明思）曾任空姐，就讀於美國艾德蒙社區學院，文學副學士畢業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/116412896_110417533992175_3090216070154516080_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2F116412896_110417533992175_3090216070154516080_n_600.jpg&h=7256efe0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72da8cea6dfe444f2c7f7fb7c74071a28b396bbd","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":129,"dislike":3,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T15:11:26.000Z","msg":"14.蘇玉華<br />\n<br />\n蘇玉華中七畢業，後於國泰航空任空姐9個月，當時覺得該工種並不符自己性格、個性，於是報讀演藝學院，畢業入行做演員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783886/6188618ac133f5561bfabd4d7f86396c_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783886%2F6188618ac133f5561bfabd4d7f86396c_600.jpg&h=0ec94481&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf0ba314d1f662ef0799f5f785cb8ddb7e662dd4","tid":2254134,"uid":44730,"like":24,"dislike":12,"score":12,"citedB